x1 y1 lineto closepath } def
/OvalFrame { x1 x2 eq y1 y2 eq or { pop pop x1 y1 moveto x2 y2 L } { y1
y2 sub abs x1 x2 sub abs 2 copy gt { exch pop } { pop } ifelse 2 div
